    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_1_756-790",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "756-790",
      "markText": "典冠举衣以复韩侯，虽越职之罪难逃；野人美芹而献于君，亦爱主之诚可取。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=756&rangeEnd=790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=756&rangeEnd=790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_5_0-60",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "0-60",
      "markText": "臣闻今之论天下者皆曰：“南北有定势，吴楚之脆弱不足以争衡于中原。”臣之说曰：“古今有常理，夷狄之腥秽不可以久安于华夏。”",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_6_0-27",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "0-27",
      "markText": "臣闻用兵之道，无所不备则有所必分，知所必守则不必皆备。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_1_194-240",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "194-240",
      "markText": "臣常鸠众二千，逮耿京，为掌书记，与图恢夏，共籍兵二十五万，纳款于朝。不幸变生肘腋，事乃大谬。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=194&rangeEnd=240",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=194&rangeEnd=240"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_3_0-64",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "0-64",
      "markText": "两敌相持，无以得其情则疑，疑故易骇，骇而应之必不能详；有以得其情则定，定故不可惑，不可惑而听彼之自扰，则权常在我而敌实受其弊矣。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_3_64-102",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "64-102",
      "markText": "古之善用兵者，非能务为必胜，而能谋为不可胜。盖不可胜者乃所以徐图必胜之功也。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=64&rangeEnd=102",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=64&rangeEnd=102"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_3_189-202",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "189-202",
      "markText": "权然后知轻重，度而后知长短",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=189&rangeEnd=202",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=189&rangeEnd=202"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_3_1010-1029",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1010-1029",
      "markText": "且彼诚欲战耶，则必不肯张皇以速我之备。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1010&rangeEnd=1029",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1010&rangeEnd=1029"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_11_39-49",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "39-49",
      "markText": "我无尔诈，尔无我虞。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=39&rangeEnd=49",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=39&rangeEnd=49"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_1_517-550",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "517-550",
      "markText": "恭惟皇帝陛下。聪明神武，灼见事机，虽光武明谋，宪宗果断，所难比拟。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=517&rangeEnd=550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=517&rangeEnd=550"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_4_881-946",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "881-946",
      "markText": "孟子曰：“为汤武驱民者，桀与纣也。”臣亦谓今之中原离合之衅已开，虏人不动则已，诚动焉，是特为陛下驱民而已。惟静以待之，彼不亡何待！",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=881&rangeEnd=946",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=881&rangeEnd=946"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_1_735-746",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "735-746",
      "markText": "雪耻酬百王，除凶报千古",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=735&rangeEnd=746",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=735&rangeEnd=746"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_9_137-194",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "137-194",
      "markText": "一夫不平，输情于敌，则吾之所忌彼知而投之，吾之所长彼习而用之；投吾所忌，用吾所长，是殆益敌资而遗敌胜耳，不可不察。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=137&rangeEnd=194",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=137&rangeEnd=194"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_1_62-76",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "62-76",
      "markText": "受廛济南，代膺阃寄荷国厚恩。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=62&rangeEnd=76",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=62&rangeEnd=76"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_2_0-55",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "0-55",
      "markText": "用兵之道，形与势二。不知而一之，则沮于形、昡于势，而胜不可图，且坐受毙矣。何谓形？小大是也。何谓势？虚实是也。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_3_378-425",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "378-425",
      "markText": "譬如狩狗焉，心不肯自闲，击不则吠，吠而后却；呼之则驯，驯必致啮。盖吠我者忌我也，驯我者狎我也。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=378&rangeEnd=425",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=378&rangeEnd=425"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_4_0-55",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "0-55",
      "markText": "自古天下离合之势常系乎民心，民心叛服之由实基于喜怒。喜怒之方形，视之若未有休戚；喜怒之积，离合始决而不可制矣。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "789577_4_590-620",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "590-620",
      "markText": "此机不一再，而朝廷虑不及此，中原义兵寻亦溃散。吁！甚可追惜也",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=789577&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=590&rangeEnd=620",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da327605c0c490da6f13a4?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=590&rangeEnd=620"
    },
    {
